('Cafe', 'CRAFT', 'กรุุงเทพ', 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/wQVjQtDJLnKerfBD9', 'https://bit.ly/GGCRAFT', 'CRAFT is your coffee go-to with single origin and blends stemming from Thailand’s incredible coffee landscape. Working with Karo Coffee Roasters, we are serving their premium coffee beans which are exclusively available for Kimpton Maa-Lai Bangkok. Carefully handpicked from the highlands of Nan province, it’s all about locally sourced, locally loved.

Spend your mornings sitting at the counter and watching our baristas in action, with a cup of our specialty coffee in hand. Grab a bite from our extensive all-day menu, as we offer you local and international daily specials.

At night, switch round to the other side of the bar and treat yourself to our signature cocktail (or two!). If it’s the other brew you’re after, we also have local and international beers on tap, all paired with easy eats and a curated music vibe.

Being a pet-friendly café in Bangkok, CRAFT proudly welcomes your four-legged, furry companions. Hang out on our outdoor terrace, complete with a lush garden that is perfect for walkies!', NULL, NULL, 'สามารถพาสัตว์เลี้ยงเข้าได้', 13.765708, 100.495371),
